{"tid":1846465,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑老母有妄想症","createTime":"2020-01-27T15:34:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T10:22:44.000Z","uid":101600,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b813e9af735ca9209b9709e59fb1be166fc989c3","tid":1846465,"uid":101600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:34:15.000Z","msg":"懷疑老母有妄想症<br />\n<br />\n冇記錯好似前年定上年<br />\n咪好多市民屋企門口俾人寫標記<br />\n用來表示有冇人係屋企方便爆格<br />\n<br />\n電視報道完之後幾個月老母就話成日話有好多個鏡頭影住佢<br />\n<br />\n一開始<br />\n1. 話對面棟大廈同一層有個大鏡頭成日影住佢<br />\n我老母成日心驚驚喺度嘈 成日手指指嗰個位置有鏡頭<br />\n我用過強光照射嗰位置根本就係一個抽氣扇而唔係一個鏡頭<br />\n<br />\n同佢講過好多次 但佢死都話有人影住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自此就開始一個月有幾日會咁樣講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 冇幾耐之後開始話對面屋企嗰家人用三個鏡頭影住佢 我自己睇過根本冇<br />\n有一次佢趁對面果家人揼垃圾<br />\n走去鬧人地做咩攞鏡頭影住佢<br />\n對面家人兩個80幾歲嘅公公婆婆 有陣時佢個仔會帶個孫過嚟玩幾日<br />\n當住我老母面前講根本就冇影佢 我嗰陣時都入埋去望吓根本就冇任何嘅鏡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身對面果家人都同我好熟 都好好人<br />\n治安好好冇必要裝cam<br />\n<br />\n3. 今次就話對面3樓用平板電腦開閃光燈影佢<br />\n喺度口噏噏話對面有六個鏡頭<br />\n好肉緊咁喺度講 一個 兩個 三個 呢一邊又有 一個 兩個 三個 總共六個鏡頭影住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭先無意中望到對面嗰個磨砂玻璃位置 上邊有個抽氣扇應該係廁所 閂咗窗 見到佢反咗兩次光 望清楚啲似係鏡櫃打開閂埋造成嘅反光<br />\n<br />\n其實一開始已經佢買咗好多窗簾<br />\n差唔多全間屋嘅窗遮住曬<br />\n後尾同佢傾先至肯買番啲透光嘅<br />\n<br />\n我可以點做<br />\n又唔覺得佢嚴重到要睇心理醫生<br />\n始終心理醫生都係開藥比佢 貴之外仲傷身體<br />\n但最主要覺得冇影響佢生活 係間唔中一個月有幾日喺度講<br />\n都唔知有咩方法 唉"},{"pid":"2ee6714af74be7676b19d7929edf2b4c0a0fee6f","tid":1846465,"uid":307619,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:36:39.000Z","msg":"應該係思覺失調嘅其中一種<br />\n睇下呢條link邊個地區幫到<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swd.gov.hk/tc/index/site_pubsvc/page_rehab/sub_listofserv/id_supportcom/id_iccmw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Findex%2Fsite_pubsvc%2Fpage_rehab%2Fsub_listofserv%2Fid_supportcom%2Fid_iccmw%2F&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5qZPNspveiVXvfzVSLwjqls%3D&h=78eecab8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.swd.gov.hk/tc/index/site_pubsvc/page_rehab/sub_listofserv/id_supportcom/id_iccmw/</a>"},{"pid":"000ba3ee4c2a1ce9b7b79eb14f349f1101948b07","tid":1846465,"uid":101600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ee6714af74be7676b19d7929edf2b4c0a0fee6f","tid":1846465,"uid":307619,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:36:39.000Z","msg":"應該係思覺失調嘅其中一種<br />\n睇下呢條link邊個地區幫到<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swd.gov.hk/tc/index/site_pubsvc/page_rehab/sub_listofserv/id_supportcom/id_iccmw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Findex%2Fsite_pubsvc%2Fpage_rehab%2Fsub_listofserv%2Fid_supportcom%2Fid_iccmw%2F&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5qZPNspveiVXvfzVSLwjqls%3D&h=78eecab8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.swd.gov.hk/tc/index/site_pubsvc/page_rehab/sub_listofserv/id_supportcom/id_iccmw/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:41:03.000Z","msg":"但佢成日好似好委屈咁講<br />\n驚我哋有咩事有黑社會搞我地<br />\n<br />\n唔知點樣引導佢去見社工<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81599ee8fd0d171f50b03d6b826541b2d2b3ff14","tid":1846465,"uid":202106,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:45:16.000Z","msg":"葵涌醫院幫到您"},{"pid":"d86c7718372046b38a0d4af871870ddb2b304da4","tid":1846465,"uid":107686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:47:40.000Z","msg":"病向淺中醫啊"},{"pid":"a6283b1fcf5eac773e179d742253416ca2521c68","tid":1846465,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:50:27.000Z","msg":"幾歲先老人進入衰退期冇得醫嫁"},{"pid":"01f2b9933bcc2573d72bd984cb2cb511aaa2458d","tid":1846465,"uid":134744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:50:38.000Z","msg":"應該係以前中過招有陰影<br />\n睇下心理醫生搵番發生過咩事好啲<br />\n如果唔係只會越黎越嚴重"},{"pid":"84fc9274ad87e80d6e79aabd4bbb342aba28e55f","tid":1846465,"uid":193904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:51:05.000Z","msg":"1）佢係擔心影佢d乜嘢？<br />\n2）有無曾經真係比人偷過野/偷影過？"},{"pid":"a15b8bd977457b81b7a282dd9fa5d956d20e4ccf","tid":1846465,"uid":23735,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:54:17.000Z","msg":"過來人答你 我老母都係有思覺失調 拖左好耐先去睇醫生 越拖得耐 佢只會越黎越嚴重 家人都會越黎越辛苦 唔好覺得問題唔嚴重就唔睇醫生 始終都係精神病 你永遠唔知佢會幾時惡化 有機會傷害自己傷害身邊既人"},{"pid":"4ac6447c1e20d2aa5267e6f6f3891df568976b8f","tid":1846465,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"000ba3ee4c2a1ce9b7b79eb14f349f1101948b07","tid":1846465,"uid":101600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ee6714af74be7676b19d7929edf2b4c0a0fee6f","tid":1846465,"uid":307619,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:36:39.000Z","msg":"應該係思覺失調嘅其中一種<br />\n睇下呢條link邊個地區幫到<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swd.gov.hk/tc/index/site_pubsvc/page_rehab/sub_listofserv/id_supportcom/id_iccmw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Findex%2Fsite_pubsvc%2Fpage_rehab%2Fsub_listofserv%2Fid_supportcom%2Fid_iccmw%2F&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5qZPNspveiVXvfzVSLwjqls%3D&h=78eecab8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.swd.gov.hk/tc/index/site_pubsvc/page_rehab/sub_listofserv/id_supportcom/id_iccmw/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:41:03.000Z","msg":"但佢成日好似好委屈咁講<br />\n驚我哋有咩事有黑社會搞我地<br />\n<br />\n唔知點樣引導佢去見社工<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:55:15.000Z","msg":"氹佢講啲社工都遇過呢啲情況<br />\n叫佢當係傾吓計咁<br />\n唔好當佢係有問題要見社工"},{"pid":"46dfea99d543b17e99f52b99c2ea773466d15d1a","tid":1846465,"uid":225067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:57:31.000Z","msg":"應該係身體出左問題 令佢出現妄想<br />\n趁佢仲未開始有幻覺 情況未惡化之前快d帶佢去睇醫生<br />\n唔一定要入院 食住d藥睇下情況有冇好轉先 呢d唔拖得"},{"pid":"738f91c22178cfd1f188056301c19f09d1f005d8","tid":1846465,"uid":164932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:00:07.000Z","msg":"幾歲 有機會係腦退化先兆"},{"pid":"163